{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-novel-version-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon; Novel Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-05",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/themaltesefalconnovel_2603_librivox/maltesefalcon_05_hammett_128kb.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "The Levantine",
  "reader_name": "NLizer",
  "page_num": 2,
  "page_total": 4,
  "page_start_sec": 279.648,
  "page_end_sec": 521.36,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.679,
  "corrected": "claude",
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 279.648,
      "end": 281.0,
      "text": "Besides the wallet and its contents,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 281.42,
      "end": 283.62,
      "text": "there were three gaily colored silk handkerchiefs,"
    },
    {
      "start": 283.68,
      "end": 284.96,
      "text": "fragrant of _chypre_,"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.64,
      "end": 287.38,
      "text": "a platinum Longines watch"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.64,
      "end": 290.48,
      "text": "on a platinum and red gold chain, attached at"
    },
    {
      "start": 290.48,
      "end": 292.46,
      "text": "the other end to a small pear-shaped pendant"
    },
    {
      "start": 293.16,
      "end": 294.06,
      "text": "of some white metal,"
    },
    {
      "start": 294.55,
      "end": 296.3,
      "text": "a handful of United States,"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.34,
      "end": 296.7,
      "text": "British,"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.88,
      "end": 297.24,
      "text": "French,"
    },
    {
      "start": 297.3,
      "end": 298.22,
      "text": "and Chinese coins,"
    },
    {
      "start": 298.7,
      "end": 300.6,
      "text": "a ring holding half a dozen keys,"
    },
    {
      "start": 301.5,
      "end": 303.32,
      "text": "a silver and onyx fountain-pen,"
    },
    {
      "start": 304.34,
      "end": 305.6,
      "text": "a metal comb in a leatherette"
    },
    {
      "start": 305.74,
      "end": 306.02,
      "text": "case,"
    },
    {
      "start": 306.8,
      "end": 308.7,
      "text": "a nail-file in a leatherette case,"
    },
    {
      "start": 308.97,
      "end": 311.28,
      "text": "a small street-guide to San Francisco,"
    },
    {
      "start": 312.26,
      "end": 313.08,
      "text": "a Southern Pacific"
    },
    {
      "start": 313.34,
      "end": 314.04,
      "text": "baggage-check,"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.02,
      "end": 317.12,
      "text": "a half-filled package of violet pastilles,"
    },
    {
      "start": 317.52,
      "end": 320.08,
      "text": "a Shanghai insurance-broker's business-"
    },
    {
      "start": 320.08,
      "end": 320.54,
      "text": "card;"
    },
    {
      "start": 320.82,
      "end": 323.76,
      "text": "and four sheets of Hotel Belvedere writing paper,"
    },
    {
      "start": 324.38,
      "end": 326.24,
      "text": "on one of which was written in small,"
    },
    {
      "start": 326.42,
      "end": 327.14,
      "text": "precise letters,"
    },
    {
      "start": 327.4,
      "end": 329.96,
      "text": "Samuel Spade's name and the addresses"
    },
    {
      "start": 329.96,
      "end": 331.9,
      "text": "of his office and his apartment."
    },
    {
      "start": 332.96,
      "end": 334.66,
      "text": "Having examined these articles carefully—",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 335.04,
      "end": 337.06,
      "text": "he even opened the back of the watch-case"
    },
    {
      "start": 337.06,
      "end": 338.72,
      "text": "to see that nothing was hidden inside—"
    },
    {
      "start": 339.84,
      "end": 342.34,
      "text": "Spade leaned over and took the unconscious man's wrist"
    },
    {
      "start": 342.52,
      "end": 343.68,
      "text": "between finger and thumb,"
    },
    {
      "start": 343.86,
      "end": 344.92,
      "text": "feeling his pulse."
    },
    {
      "start": 345.92,
      "end": 346.76,
      "text": "Then he dropped the wrist,"
    },
    {
      "start": 346.96,
      "end": 348.26,
      "text": "settled back in his chair,"
    },
    {
      "start": 348.8,
      "end": 350.35,
      "text": "and rolled and lighted another cigarette."
    },
    {
      "start": 351.36,
      "end": 351.78,
      "text": "His face,"
    },
    {
      "start": 351.78,
      "end": 352.36,
      "text": "while he smoked,"
    },
    {
      "start": 352.84,
      "end": 354.58,
      "text": "was, except for occasional slight"
    },
    {
      "start": 354.7,
      "end": 356.42,
      "text": "and aimless movements of his lower lip,"
    },
    {
      "start": 356.98,
      "end": 359.3,
      "text": "so still and reflective that it seemed stupid;"
    },
    {
      "start": 359.8,
      "end": 363.22,
      "text": "but when Cairo presently moaned and fluttered his eyelids,"
    },
    {
      "start": 363.968,
      "end": 365.22,
      "text": "Spade's face became bland,"
    },
    {
      "start": 366.0,
      "end": 369.16,
      "text": "and he put the beginning of a friendly smile into his eyes and mouth."
    },
    {
      "start": 370.336,
      "end": 371.64,
      "text": "Joel Cairo awakened slowly.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 372.3,
      "end": 373.32,
      "text": "His eyes opened first,"
    },
    {
      "start": 373.92,
      "end": 375.66,
      "text": "but a full minute passed before they fixed"
    },
    {
      "start": 375.66,
      "end": 378.08,
      "text": "their gaze on any definite part of the ceiling."
    },
    {
      "start": 379.06,
      "end": 380.36,
      "text": "Then he shut his mouth and swallowed,"
    },
    {
      "start": 380.76,
      "end": 383.06,
      "text": "exhaling heavily through his nose afterward."
    },
    {
      "start": 384.04,
      "end": 387.22,
      "text": "He drew in one foot and turned a hand over on his thigh."
    },
    {
      "start": 388.14,
      "end": 389.82,
      "text": "Then he raised his head from the chair-back,"
    },
    {
      "start": 390.5,
      "end": 391.96,
      "text": "looked around the office in confusion,"
    },
    {
      "start": 392.82,
      "end": 393.44,
      "text": "saw Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 393.58,
      "end": 394.34,
      "text": "and sat up."
    },
    {
      "start": 394.82,
      "end": 396.5,
      "text": "He opened his mouth to speak,"
    },
    {
      "start": 396.7,
      "end": 397.28,
      "text": "started,"
    },
    {
      "start": 397.9,
      "end": 399.52,
      "text": "clapped a hand to his face where"
    },
    {
      "start": 399.6,
      "end": 403.69,
      "text": "Spade's fist had struck and where there was now a florid bruise."
    },
    {
      "start": 404.928,
      "end": 406.02,
      "text": "Cairo said through his teeth,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 406.14,
      "end": 406.52,
      "text": "painfully:"
    },
    {
      "start": 406.72,
      "end": 408.24,
      "text": "\"I could have shot you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 408.3,
      "end": 408.5,
      "text": "Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 408.6,
      "end": 409.08,
      "text": "Spade.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 409.46,
      "end": 410.82,
      "text": "\"You could have tried,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 411.06,
      "end": 412.08,
      "text": "Spade conceded."
    },
    {
      "start": 412.35,
      "end": 413.64,
      "text": "\"I did not try.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 414.0,
      "end": 415.06,
      "text": "\"I know.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 416.36,
      "end": 418.64,
      "text": "\"Then why did you strike me after I was disarmed?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 419.42,
      "end": 419.9,
      "text": "\"Sorry,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 420.08,
      "end": 420.82,
      "text": "Spade said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 421.04,
      "end": 422.44,
      "text": "and grinned wolfishly,"
    },
    {
      "start": 422.46,
      "end": 423.66,
      "text": "showing his jaw-teeth,"
    },
    {
      "start": 424.66,
      "end": 426.26,
      "text": "\"but imagine my embarrassment when I"
    },
    {
      "start": 426.26,
      "end": 429.04,
      "text": "found that five-thousand-dollar offer was just hooey.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 430.24,
      "end": 430.74,
      "text": "\"You are mistaken,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 430.92,
      "end": 431.1,
      "text": "Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 431.22,
      "end": 431.62,
      "text": "Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 431.84,
      "end": 432.3,
      "text": "That was,"
    },
    {
      "start": 432.48,
      "end": 433.0,
      "text": "and is,"
    },
    {
      "start": 433.2,
      "end": 434.14,
      "text": "a genuine offer.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 435.46,
      "end": 435.94,
      "text": "\"What the hell?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 436.576,
      "end": 437.76,
      "text": "Spade's surprise was genuine."
    },
    {
      "start": 438.94,
      "end": 442.18,
      "text": "\"I am prepared to pay five thousand dollars for the figure's return.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 443.712,
      "end": 445.32,
      "text": "Cairo took his hand away from his bruised"
    },
    {
      "start": 445.32,
      "end": 447.4,
      "text": "face and sat up prim and business-like again."
    },
    {
      "start": 448.18,
      "end": 448.82,
      "text": "\"You have it?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 449.38,
      "end": 450.04,
      "text": "\"No.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 451.52,
      "end": 452.34,
      "text": "\"If it is not here\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 452.6,
      "end": 454.62,
      "text": "—Cairo was very politely skeptical—"
    },
    {
      "start": 455.9,
      "end": 457.06,
      "text": "\"why should you have risked serious"
    },
    {
      "start": 457.06,
      "end": 459.08,
      "text": "injury to prevent my searching for it?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 460.42,
      "end": 463.32,
      "text": "\"I should sit around and let people come in and stick me up?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 464.576,
      "end": 467.28,
      "text": "Spade flicked a finger at Cairo's possessions on the desk."
    },
    {
      "start": 468.24,
      "end": 469.34,
      "text": "\"You've got my apartment-address."
    },
    {
      "start": 469.7,
      "end": 470.6,
      "text": "Been up there yet?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 471.17,
      "end": 472.02,
      "text": "\"Yes,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 472.24,
      "end": 472.48,
      "text": "Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 472.6,
      "end": 472.94,
      "text": "Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 473.34,
      "end": 476.2,
      "text": "I am ready to pay five thousand dollars for the figure's return,"
    },
    {
      "start": 476.68,
      "end": 479.58,
      "text": "but surely it is natural enough that I should try first"
    },
    {
      "start": 479.7,
      "end": 481.64,
      "text": "to spare the owner that expense if possible.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 482.61,
      "end": 483.4,
      "text": "\"Who is he?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 484.896,
      "end": 486.08,
      "text": "Cairo shook his head and smiled.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 487.14,
      "end": 489.38,
      "text": "\"You will have to forgive my not answering that question.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 490.46,
      "end": 490.78,
      "text": "\"Will I?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 491.68,
      "end": 492.42,
      "text": "Spade leaned forward,"
    },
    {
      "start": 492.5,
      "end": 493.6,
      "text": "smiling with tight lips."
    },
    {
      "start": 494.62,
      "end": 495.54,
      "text": "\"I've got you by the neck,"
    },
    {
      "start": 495.64,
      "end": 495.94,
      "text": "Cairo."
    },
    {
      "start": 496.48,
      "end": 499.16,
      "text": "You've walked in and tied yourself up, plenty strong enough"
    },
    {
      "start": 499.3,
      "end": 501.58,
      "text": "to suit the police, with last night's killings."
    },
    {
      "start": 501.7,
      "end": 501.8,
      "text": "Well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 502.68,
      "end": 504.8,
      "text": "now you'll have to play with me or else.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 506.112,
      "end": 509.22,
      "text": "Cairo's smile was demure and not in any way alarmed.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 510.14,
      "end": 511.79,
      "text": "\"I made somewhat extensive inquiries"
    },
    {
      "start": 511.98,
      "end": 513.52,
      "text": "about you before taking any action,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 513.58,
      "end": 513.94,
      "text": "he said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 514.1,
      "end": 517.26,
      "text": "\"and was assured that you were far too reasonable to"
    },
    {
      "start": 517.38,
      "end": 519.58,
      "text": "allow other considerations to interfere"
    },
    {
      "start": 519.58,
      "end": 521.36,
      "text": "with profitable business relations.\""
    }
  ]
}